title: Hogmanay 2013 Live - BBC Scotland - New Year
description:
Hogmanay Live from Edinburgh, Scotland - with Jackie Bird


Jackie Bird leads the countdown to 2014 from Edinburgh's Princes Street and finds out how the New Year is being celebrated around the country, including reports from the Old Fruitmarket in Glasgow and Stirling Castle. Featuring a special message from Rab C Nesbitt, an acoustic performance by Biffy Clyro and live music by Phil Cunningham and Aly Bain, Deacon Blue, John McCusker, Heidi Talbot, Roddy Hart and the Lonesome Fire, and the Boghall and Bathgate Caledonia Pipe Band, plus the traditional nationwide Auld Lang Syne singalong


Category General Show
